 of the cycle
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
. "Fan Tai Suei" means your birth year\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s zodiac animal is same
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 as the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Tai Suei\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66s
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 for that exact
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 year. If you happen to have the same zodiac animal
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 as the
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Tia Suei, you would need to An Tai Suei
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 that
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 year for good fortune. The second custom is "Bai Dou." Dou means
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 light. Everybody knows that
