 can\uc2 \u8217\'81\'66t be put
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 out for
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 the entire year. Bai Dou is also a way to wish for
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 blessing. Many temples have this ceremony. Some Dou is for family, and some
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 is
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 for
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 individual
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
s. Family Dou
