 be more expensive because you
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 can
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 write more names on it.
}
\par \pard\plain \s21\ql\nowidctlpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa0\ltrpar\cf0\dbch\af6\langfe2052\dbch\af5\afs20\alang1081\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch \~}

{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
The third custom is the "Light of Guang
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 Ming,"
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 which is also called the "Light of Gung Ming
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
," when performed for a
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 different
}{\cf2\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 purpose.
}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
 If you
